Package hamlet.alexander.SpeakEasy

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • hamlet.alexander.SpeakEasy.User
  • public class User
extends java.lang.Object
    User model. Stores user's username, password, and their role for permissions. This class is used to both hold user information for the current applications session as well as store user data in the database.
